func:
msg.payload = {
    layer: "aircrafts",
    lat: msg.payload.geometry.coordinates[1],
    lon: msg.payload.geometry.coordinates[0],
    heading: msg.payload.properties.heading,
    speed: msg.payload.properties.speed/10.0,
    tooltip: msg.payload.properties.ident,
    label: msg.payload.properties.flight.callsign,
    icon: "plane",
    iconColor: msg.payload.properties.flight.is_arrival ? "#00DD00" : "#FF85FF",
    ttl: 60*60*2,
    name: msg.payload.properties.icao24
}

return msg;
